---
// Brief value-proposition section between Hero and Features.
// Lives between the emotional pull of the hero and the concrete feature
// cards: gives the visitor a one-paragraph "what is this exactly?"
---

<section class="value-prop" aria-labelledby="value-prop-title">
    <div class="container value-prop-inner">
        <p class="value-prop-eyebrow">Qué estamos armando</p>
        <h2 id="value-prop-title" class="value-prop-title">
            Tu próxima escapada al Litoral, sin vueltas
        </h2>
        <p class="value-prop-body">
            Estamos juntando a los mejores anfitriones de Concepción del Uruguay y
            la región. Cabañas frente al río, hosterías de campo, casas para
            escaparte el fin de semana — todo en un solo lugar, con precios claros
            y reserva directa.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .value-prop {
        background: var(--core-background);
        padding-block: var(--space-section);
    }

    .value-prop-inner {
        max-width: 720px;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .value-prop-eyebrow {
        font-size: var(--text-body-sm);
        font-weight: 500;
        letter-spacing: 0.12em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--hospeda-river);
        margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
    }

    .value-prop-title {
        font-size: var(--text-display);
        margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
        max-width: 18ch;
        margin-inline: auto;
    }

    .value-prop-body {
        font-size: var(--text-tagline);
        color: var(--core-muted-foreground);
        max-width: 56ch;
        margin-inline: auto;
        line-height: 1.7;
    }
</style>
